#. Max bytes: 82
msgctxt "Offset_0x3239C_Len_82"
msgid ""
"(Is this the father of the kid Taichi hurt?\n"
"I'm pretty sure his name is Ishigaki.)"
msgstr ""
"(È il padre del bimbo ferito da Taichi?\n"
"Credo si chiami Ishigaki.)"

#. Max bytes: 75
msgctxt "Offset_0x33340_Len_75"
msgid ""
"(I need to make sure they have enough\n"
"to cover their son's hospital bills.)"
msgstr ""
"(Devo accertarmi che abbiano soldi\n"
"per le cure in ospedale del figlio.)"

#. Max bytes: 54
msgctxt "Offset_0x33480_Len_54"
msgid ""
"(More importantly, I can't let\n"
"Taichi end up in debt!)"
msgstr ""
"(Soprattutto, Taichi non\n"
"può finire nei debiti!)"

#. Max bytes: 18
msgctxt "Offset_0x3AD8C_Len_18"
msgid "(This is weird...)"
msgstr "(È strano...)"

#. Max bytes: 58
msgctxt "Offset_0x3B598_Len_58"
msgid ""
"(Something seems wrong about this...\n"
"It has to be a scam.)"
msgstr ""
"(C'è qualcosa che non va...\n"
"Deve essere una truffa.)"

#. Max bytes: 39
msgctxt "Offset_0x3B6B8_Len_39"
msgid "(I should try to catch him in his lie.)"
msgstr "(Dovrei farlo cadere in trappola.)"

#. Max bytes: 54
msgctxt "Offset_0x3BEFC_Len_54"
msgid "(This must be the guy that fake Taichi told me about.)"
msgstr ""
"(Deve essere il tizio del\n"
"finto Taichi.)"

#. Max bytes: 10
msgctxt "Offset_0x3E244_Len_10"
msgid "(Got him.)"
msgstr "(Preso.)"

#. Max bytes: 29
msgctxt "Offset_0x79CA8_Len_29"
msgid "I should hand over the money."
msgstr "Dovrei dare i soldi."

#. Max bytes: 15
msgctxt "Offset_0x79CE8_Len_15"
msgid "This is a scam!"
msgstr "È una truffa!"

